      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Mathematics &amp; Statistics (Sci)              : Basic point-set topology, metric spaces: open and closed sets, normed and Banach spaces, HÃ¶lder and Minkowski inequalities, sequential compactness, Heine-Borel, Banach Fixed Point theorem. Riemann-(Stieltjes) integral, Fundamental Theorem of Calculus, Taylor's theorem. Uniform convergence. Infinite series,  convergence tests, power series. Elementary functions.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Winter 2015          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Vojkan Jaksic (Winter)                  </p>

    
